RELEASE
=======

------------------
Version 1.1.5   2013-10-30

 - update chk-uname, add Marvericks
 
------------------
Version 1.1.4   2013-10-02

 - modify configure.ac for CPM special flag
 
------------------
Version 1.1.3   2013-10-02

 - modify for intel mpi
 
------------------
Version 1.1.2   2013-07-20

 - change VersionInfo()

--------------------------
Version 1.1.1   2013-07-13

 - Update configure.ac for link issue for GNU compiler
 - Update include/cpm_Version.h.in and cpm_Base.h

--------------------------
Version 1.1.0   2013-07-12

 - Edit configure.ac for a wrapper compiler, change install option

--------------------------
Version 1.0.12  2013-06-29

 - Update README, NEWS, ChangeLog, LICENSE, INSTALL, configure.ac


--------------------------
Version 1.0.11  2013-06-27

 - Change configure.ac
  - TP_CFLAGS=`$TP_DIR/bin/tp-config --cflags`
  - TP_LDFLAGS=`$TP_DIR/bin/tp-config --libs`
  - remove TP_LIBS from configure.ac & cpm-config.in
  - PM_CFLAGS=`$PM_DIR/bin/pm-config --cflags`
  - PM_LDFLAGS=`$PM_DIR/bin/pm-config --libs`
  - remove PM_LIBS from configure.ac & cpm-config.in

--------------------------
Version 1.0.10  2013-06-27

 - Add PMlib option to configure.
 - Correction of manual.
 - Correction of TextParser archive name -lTP.
 - Correction of cpm-config.
 - Correction of config_cpm.sh
 - Change archive name to libCPM.a

-------------------------
Version 1.0.9  2013-05-02

 - Add a LICENSE file.
 - Modification of User's guide.

-------------------------
Version 1.0.8  2013-04-03

 - Introduce a function of ActiveSubdomain. Following functions are added.
   cpm_ParaManager::VoxelInit_Subdomain関数追加
   cpm_GlobalDomainInfo::ReadActiveSubdomainFile()
   cpm_GlobalDomainInfo::isMatchEndianSbdmMagick()
   cpm_ParaManager::IsOuterBoundary()
   cpm_ParaManager::IsInnerBoundary()

 - Introduction of error codes.
    cpm_Define.h
    CPM_ERROR_OPEN_SBDM             =3012
    CPM_ERROR_READ_SBDM_HEADER      =3013
    CPM_ERROR_READ_SBDM_FORMAT      =3014
    CPM_ERROR_READ_SBDM_DIV         =3015
    CPM_ERROR_READ_SBDM_CONTENTS    =3016
    CPM_ERROR_SBDM_NUMDOMAIN_ZERO   =3017
    CPM_ERROR_MISMATCH_DIV_SUBDOMAIN=3018

 - Add endian utility.
    cpm_EndianUtil.h

 - Add file path utility.
    cpm_PathUtil.h


-------------------------
Version 1.0.6  2012-08-25

 - Abolition of using REAL_TYPE
 - Correction by change of TextParser API.


-------------------------
Version 1.0.5  2012-08-04

 - Improve redundant code to automatically decide the number of division for a whole
  computational domain.

-------------------------
Version 1.0.4  2012-07-09

 - Correction of cpm-uname shell script.
 - Add description for Fortran90 compiler at configure (in User's guide).


-------------------------
Version 1.0.3  2012-07-03

 - Add GetHostName()
 - Add GetBndIndexExtGc()
 - Add figures for the description of index and original point (in User's guide).
 - Add description for CPM Op，CPM Datatype (in User's guide).


-------------------------
Version 1.0.2  2012-06-27

 - Add description of asynchronous communication (in User's guide).
 - Modification of file format for partitioning information.
 - Change specification of cpm_ParaManager::VoxelInit.


-------------------------
Version 1.0.1  2012-06-25

 - Change order of Macro;
  before
	  enum cpm_FaceFlag
	  {
	    X_MINUS = 0  ///< -X face
	  , Y_MINUS = 1  ///< -Y face
	  , Z_MINUS = 2  ///< -Z face
	  , X_PLUS  = 3  ///< +X face
	  , Y_PLUS  = 4  ///< +Y face
	  , Z_PLUS  = 5  ///< +Z face
	  };
  after
	  enum cpm_FaceFlag
	  {
	    X_MINUS = 0  ///< -X face
	  , X_PLUS  = 1  ///< +X face
	  , Y_MINUS = 2  ///< -Y face
	  , Y_PLUS  = 3  ///< +Y face
	  , Z_MINUS = 4  ///< -Z face
	  , Z_PLUS  = 5  ///< +Z face
	  };


-------------------------
Version 1.0.0  2012-06-18

 - Initial release.
